{
  "doc_id": "38618",
  "text": "Measurement of contents of resveratrol, piceid, anthocyanin and total flavonoid. The contents of resveratrol and piceid were determined using the method of Zhou, et al. [CITATION_1] . Anthocyanin levels were measured as previously described [CITATION_2] . The total flavonoid content was determined using ultraviolet spectroscopy [CITATION_3] .",
